'''Bantha bile''' was a material harvested from the [[Bantha/Legends|bantha]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Rodia/Legends|Rodia]]. It was a black-market substance that was used as a medicinal remedy.

[[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] smuggled bantha bile during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]] in containers marked with a [[Rodian/Legends|Rodian]] head icon.

